{"tid":2327830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李偲嫣fb最後一post： 黎智英快送中 #應有此報","createTime":"2020-12-16T09:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T15:26:46.000Z","uid":227801,"like":279,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"832a7569c2d4fa108bc6a9b545c26399b8c9e49e","tid":2327830,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/CVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FCVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI%2F&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=7ab77217\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201216%2FCVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI%2F&h=1c16d90e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201216/CVMDNM2YDBFGHM664GOR4GUDSI/</a><br />\n翻查李偲嫣的facebook個人專頁，最後一則帖文是上周六（12日），狠批流亡美國的梁頌恆；同日早上她亦發文諷刺被加控「勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全」提堂的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，要求盡快將黎送返中國審理及判刑，並留下hashtag 「#應有此報」、「#毒害香港」、「#支持國安法」。她的WhatsApp最後上線時間則停留在本周一（14日）早上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8P8fwgpgK60WTezwbXM-Au9sqXA=/504x675/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2KP3NFN2UZCFDGDW3NC3666YNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8P8fwgpgK60WTezwbXM-Au9sqXA%3D%2F504x675%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2KP3NFN2UZCFDGDW3NC3666YNA.jpg&h=982c2e12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93c0aa085fc3e03ff73b754a0bb8e03140544770","tid":2327830,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a706598aa5f6291686f8ec8a468be1636ba4c5a9","tid":2327830,"uid":199893,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"佢fb而家好睇了"},{"pid":"ca7a99fdee2fec23c15db2